OL,3,CSummerland commemorative services to
OL,4,Cbe held at two separate locations
OL,6,FThe 'Justice for Summerland' campaign
OL,7,Fgroup is formed by survivors and
OL,8,Fbereaved families who wish to overturn
OL,9,Fthe verdict of 'misadventure' given to
OL,10,Fall those who died in the fire.
OL,12,FThey will be gathering on what remains
OL,13,Fof the Summerland site, on the
OL,14,Fnorthern side of Douglas Promenade.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, 200 metres down the road
OL,17,FDouglas Council will be holding their
OL,18,Fown commemorative service at the
OL,19,Fmemorial.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
