OL,3,CSummerland commemorative services to
OL,4,Cbe held at two separate locations
OL,6,FIn previous years, both services have
OL,7,Fbeen held at the same time, clashing
OL,8,Fwith one another.
OL,10,FMayor of Douglas, Natalie Byron-Teare
OL,11,Fsays this year she has chosen to
OL,12,Fchange the timings of the national
OL,13,Fservice, to avoid clashing with the
OL,14,Fcommemorations taking place on the
OL,15,FSummerland site.
OL,17,FShe also confirmed that she intends to
OL,18,Fbe at both services.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
