OL,3,CSummerland commemorative services to
OL,4,Cbe held at two separate locations
OL,6,FThe national service is held annually
OL,7,Fat the official memorial, ever since
OL,8,Fits unveiling for the 40th anniversary
OL,9,Fin 2013.
OL,11,FSummerland survivor, Ruth McQuillan-
OL,12,FWilson will be laying a wreath at the
OL,13,Fnational service at the memorial on
OL,14,Fbehalf of survivors.
OL,16,FShe was just five-years-old when she
OL,17,Fwas caught in the fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
