OL,3,CSummerland commemorative services to
OL,4,Cbe held at two separate locations
OL,6,FRuth said: "I need to come here to
OL,7,Fremember that I was the lucky one,
OL,8,Fthat I made it out, and I'll never let
OL,9,Fthem be forgotten.
OL,11,F"They're just so much part of my life
OL,12,Fnow and as long as I'm able to come
OL,13,Fhere, I'll come here."
OL,15,FRuth was 'swept away' from both her
OL,16,Fparents during the panicked rush to
OL,17,Fthe exit on the night of the fire.
OL,19,FShe said: "I'll never get over that
OL,20,Ffeeling of being alone and afraid and
OL,21,FI didn't know where to go to.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
