OL,3,CSummerland commemorative services to
OL,4,Cbe held at two separate locations
OL,6,FShe was eventually reunited with her
OL,7,Fmum, but suffered with severe burns.
OL,9,F"My burns were very extensive, I've
OL,10,Fseen an awful lot of injuries that
OL,11,Fpeople have had, but my burns were
OL,12,Ffull thickness right through to the
OL,13,Fbones on the back of my legs.
OL,15,F"It all had to be reconstructed."
OL,17,FWhen asked about her thoughts on the
OL,18,Fcampaign group, and whether she
OL,19,Fconsidered the fire as an injustice,
OL,20,Fshe said: "Everyone must do what's
OL,21,Fright for them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
