OL,3,CSummerland commemorative services to
OL,4,Cbe held at two separate locations
OL,6,F"I have made my peace with what
OL,7,Fhappened, it was a long time ago, and
OL,8,Fthings were different back then.
OL,10,F"I don't feel qualified to pass
OL,11,Fcomment - they have different
OL,12,Fexperiences to me and they're doing
OL,13,Fwhat's important to them - whatever
OL,14,Fthey need to do to obtain closure."
OL,16,FThe national service at the memorial
OL,17,Fis due to start at 6.45pm, while the
OL,18,Fservice on the Summerland site will
OL,19,Fbegin at 7.00pm.
